<h4 id="german-shepherd">German Shepherd:</h4>
<p>German Shepherd is a world popular dog breed. It is very smart, loyal, confidential &amp; courageous,very intelligent dog. German Shepherd is family protective, agile breed with larger in size, muscular body along with noble character.</p>

